，被人用刀襲擊，人員趕到現場後，發現一名57歲男子胸部受傷，他清醒被送往屯門醫院。警方當日在現場拘捕一名30歲男子，他被暫控一項企圖謀殺罪，新界北總區重案組正積極調查。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯參選區議會屯門樂翠選區，同區參選的有民主黨盧俊宇，及無報稱政治聯繫的蔣靖雯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />割損左LIN頭都係謀殺"},{"pid":"c29b8da8fc1e7630bf367596e5c0948997cd676c","tid":1698912,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:57:04.000Z","msg":"要人"},{"pid":"95294f12392b901ab8114ef866355988820f9e7e","tid":1698912,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺明做9手足"},{"pid":"da25c8169d56d2f035613487e2258469a2bcf02e","tid":1698912,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:35:44.000Z","msg":"咬耳 吉到人入icu條友呢？"},{"pid":"97af8d99ee04a13669e0a687154759b15dca252a","tid":1698912,"uid":142097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:37:41.000Z","msg":"dllm 何妖"},{"pid":"5c24ffff1feeb785d81cf1bead71e5a3ce25d374","tid":1698912,"uid":142433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42ivmA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42ivmA8.jpg&h=98553976&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}